Create file with just EOF

When I create file using Vim, it puts a newline, although it is empty

$> touch empty.txt
or
$> printf "" >filename.txt
creates a file with only EOF

You can also test the contents of a file as hexadecimal output
$> hexdump filename.txt

"Enter" key or newline or Line Feed (LF) character is 	ASCII 	10.
